{"tid":1553514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[不落星條旗] 賽後檢討 - 美國各大報章是日頭版","createTime":"2019-09-08T15:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T23:03:31.000Z","uid":52658,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"64a281787c9703d137bbe179982718dd8e9f8867","tid":1553514,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T8CGy7s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT8CGy7s.png&h=91a33a54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XEU9H0S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXEU9H0S.png&h=13d960f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1Atd73.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1Atd73.png&h=3794b34a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以今日我地好成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日美國會更加大肆報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0uN3NtG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0uN3NtG.png&h=42901028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">God bless United States <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n願上帝保佑美利堅合眾國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n願星條旗永不落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f744cf1719bf2779f9c731ba67e3b2da3a11befe","tid":1553514,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd3677ed231630efc54410861bd027716eca1ac","tid":1553514,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:42:16.000Z","msg":"　「自由のために戦う香港を支持して」。若者からお年寄りまでが、米国向けに英語で叫びながら行進した。米国旗を掲げる人も多く見られた。５０歳代の男性公務員は、香港に「高度な自治」を認めた「一国二制度」が形骸化していると憤り、「今、戦い続けなければ、中国本土化がさらに進み、デモもできなくなる」と危機感をにじませた。<br />\n<br />\n　参加者らは香港と中国両政府に対し、条例改正案撤回のほか、６月から続く大規模な抗議運動への警察の対応を検証する独立調査委員会の設置や、選挙制度の民主化などを求めている。"},{"pid":"132f89254402758d03872b1ac07264705deea25f","tid":1553514,"uid":46746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"掂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aafa9f62a6a2639147033429aea43c8e1bc8c8b","tid":1553514,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee9f8322e5c717d3d44b059744d0e6392134955","tid":1553514,"uid":285915,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:34:43.000Z","msg":"最近好似好多人話英文嘅文宣唔夠，又話鬼佬想睇到啲翻譯左嘅新聞。其實又班香港人已經做緊架啦。<br />\n（跪求幫推） 其實香港有班人好努力做翻譯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545086</a><br />\n我哋網站叫<a href=\"http://guardiansofhk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguardiansofhk.com&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BgESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=61f78a84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://guardiansofhk.com</a>，我哋每日都會將香港嘅新聞翻譯再放上fb，tg，同埋twitter。小弟p牌冇得推po，唯有靠大家幫手推到外國人都知香港發生咩事。<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/pages/category/Community-Organization/BeWater-HK-2406628919558580\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fpages%2Fcategory%2FCommunity-Organization%2FBeWater-HK-2406628919558580&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BgESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=2b229c34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/pages/category/Community-Organization/BeWater-HK-2406628919558580</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/standwithhkg/?igshid=we1lffxlqh9f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fstandwithhkg%2F%3Figshid%3Dwe1lffxlqh9f